Versioned Exports: Regular snapshots in multiple formats (JSON, CSV, RDF)
API Versioning: Semantic versioning for all exposed interfaces
Migration Paths: Clear procedures for knowledge graph schema evolution
Fallback Mechanisms: Graceful degradation when components fail
